heavily from the culture of lehman brothers however the events in the movie are primarily a depiction of the actions of goldman sachs in the  comedy american film horrible bosses kenny sommerfeld mentioned that he is a yale graduate who worked for lehman brothers he was earning a high sixfigure salary but is now unable to buy even basic necessities and lives in poverty the  hbo movie too big to fail recounted the days before lehman brothers declared bankruptcy and the fallout afterward the fall of lehman brothers is depicted in the  movie the big short film where two of the characters walk around the lehman brothers offices after the bankruptcy to see the main trading floor lehman brothers is parodied in the  disney animated film zootopia which depicts a financial firm called lemming brothers staffed by lemmings principal locations first year of occupancyedit  court square montgomery alabama   liberty street new york ny   fulton street new york ny – – pearl street new york ny   exchange place new york ny   william street new york ny  one william street new york ny    water street    world financial center   seventh avenue new york ny   henry lehman established his first store location on commerce street in montgomery in  in  one year after emanuels arrival the brothers moved h lehman  bro to  court square where it remained when mayer arrived in  forming lehman brothers  designated as a landmark by the new york city landmarks preservation committee in   sales and trading personnel had been in this location since  when they were joined by the firms investment bankers and brokers see alsoedit companies portal mf global the largest wall street firm to collapse since the lehman brothers debacle in september  valukas report on the failure of lehman referencesedit  history of the lehman brothers harvard university librarylehman brothers collection retrieved    melvyn dubofsky  the oxford encyclopedia of american business labor and economic history oxford university press p