y october   business lehmans desperate housewives  vanity fair vanityfaircom retrieved    truell peter november   pettit resigns as president of lehman brothers firm the new york times   white ben de la merced michael j october   mcdade to leave barclays capital the new york times   charles gasparino july   lehman brothers to take over sg cowens brokerage division the financial express archived from the original on may   retrieved    a b christine williamson back again lehman returns to institutional management with lincoln deal purchase of fixedincome business ends year absence pensions  investments goliath retrieved    thomas landon jr july   market place lehman to buy neuberger berman for  billion the new york times   legalbusinessonlinecomau legalbusinessonlinecomau september   retrieved  dead link  bill egbert september   lehman checks into sheraton daily news nydailynewscom archived from the original on may   retrieved    cast study lehman brothers pdf citrixcom  archived from the original pdf on  retrieved    williams mark april   uncontrolled risk mcgrawhill education p  isbn    williams mark april   uncontrolled risk mcgrawhill education p  isbn    mark trumbull march   lehman bros used accounting trick amid financial crisis – and earlier the christian science monitor csmonitorcom retrieved    kulikowski laura august   lehman brothers amputates mortgage arm thestreetcom retrieved    a b c anderson jenny dash eric august   struggling lehman plans to lay off  the new york times   a b katie benner september   i was lucky to get out fortune cnnmoney retrieved    a b sexist language npr ombudsman june   retrieved    a b sellers patricia march   the fall of a wall street highflier fortune cnnmoney archived from the original on december   retrieved    onaran yalman helyar john december   the fall of lehman bros  part  the new zealand herald   anderson jenny thomas landon jr august   lehman’s shares gain on signs of raising capital the new york times   morcroft gre